main event: Multiple sightings of unidentified flying objects (UFOs), with reports including high altitude objects revolving, oscillating, and blinking intermittently with red and green lights.
interesting points: Objects were observed to have changed direction, speed, size, color, and brightness, as well as flicker, throb, pulsate, and emit smoke.
Witnesses reported objects flying at very high altitudes, with estimated speeds of 3-4 times that of jet planes.
One sighting recorded strange aircraft flying 8 to 10 times as high as the world star, with multiple witnesses corroborating the observation.
Reports described luminous objects, bright and intensely glowing, without visible smoke trails or light rays.
An air intelligence report from Middletown, Pennsylvania noted the observation of an unidentified flying object, with no conclusive explanation provided.
sighted object: unidentified flying objects (UFOs) with various characteristics such as high altitude, revolving, blinking lights, and intense brightness
location: Los Angeles, CA and Middletown, PA
photographs: The report does not mention the presence of photographs
